<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā malīka ạl̊maj̊di fī mil̊ʾi ạlzãmān̊
 fīka bāna ạl̊ḥubũ fī ạảj̊lay̱ bayān̊
 kaẙfa ʿisẖ̊ta kāl̊faqīri wāl̊muhān̊
 mā laka qaṭũ maqaruⁿ̃ ạảẘ makān̊
 taṣ̊naʿu ạl̊kẖaẙra watuẓ̊hiru ạl̊ḥanān̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: yā jamīʿa ạl̊mū̊̉minīna ḥamĩdūhu
   biạb̊tihāji ạl̊qal̊bi daẘmaⁿạ wāʿ̊budūhu
   wādẖ̊kurūạ faḍ̊lạaⁿ lirabĩy radĩdūhu
   hātifīna kulã ḥīniⁿ majĩdūhu
   biạl̊masīḥi yaʿ̊ẓumu ạn̊tiṣārunā

[V2]
 2- qad̊ ḥamal̊ta rabãnā ạl̊ʿāra ạl̊mudẖīb̊
 wāḥ̊tamal̊ta gẖaḍaba ạl̊ʿad̊li ạlrãhīb̊
 yaẘma dẖuq̊ta ạl̊maẘta ʿanãạ biạlṣãlīb̊
 muẓ̊hiraⁿạ ḥubaⁿ̃ạ waʿaṭ̊faⁿạ yā ḥabīb̊
 fākẖ̊taṭaf̊ta ạlnãf̊sa min̊ jaẘfi ạllãhīb̊</lyrics>
<title>yạ mlyk ạlmjd fy mlʾ ạlzmạn</title>
</song>